{"tid":509596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"槍殺同袍平民 湖南國保遭特警生擒","createTime":"2017-12-25T13:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T02:00:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"71fa37c0dcdaf996ace51b29d359935ce922fc8a","tid":509596,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171225/20254878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171225%2F20254878&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPQtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=e6d4345d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171225%2F20254878&h=840f5e91\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171225/20254878</a><br />\n<br />\n槍殺同袍平民<br />\n湖南國保遭特警生擒<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n湖南新化縣公安國保警員陳建湘前日槍殺同袍及平民後持槍潛逃，經當局大陣仗圍堵搜捕，終在昨天下午於新化縣科頭鄉被生擒落網，當局現場撿獲一把77手槍及兩個彈夾；拘捕過程無公安傷亡。網傳影片可見陳犯滿臉血痕，右臉血肉模糊，被十多名公安特警帶着警犬圍拍團體照，如捕獲獵物般興奮。<br />\n46歲的陳建湘前日犯案後潛匿於科頭鄉三板橋村一帶，大批軍警荷槍實彈圍捕。昨午5時許特警及十多隻警犬在山坡上的石縫中發現疑兇，大聲喊話：「把手舉起來，不許動，慢慢爬下走出來！」陳犯出來後警員警犬一擁而上，將他壓在大石上，並質詢其槍枝在哪裏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171225/large/a0806a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171225%2Flarge%2Fa0806a.gif&h=fd570aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳建湘被多名警員合力制服。<br />\n<br />\n滿臉血痕　血肉模糊<br />\n<br />\n隨後特警在陳犯身上搜出兩個彈夾及附近草叢中搜索到一把77式手槍。當局稱，陳犯臉上血痕並非抓捕過程造成，特警押走疑犯途中，「看我看我！我們再來一張」，10名特警帶着警犬跟陳在現場拍團體照。隨後他被押送到新化縣人民醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n前日下午陳建湘槍殺兩人後潛逃，傳他留下筆記點名要槍殺幾十人，大部份是當地公安頭目，包括公安局長、派出所長等。當局其後稱，兩名被他開槍打死者，分別是縣教育局工作人員及下崗職工，疑與陳犯有小過節。當地居民指陳曾任派出所副所長，「比較隨和，對人很好」，認為他是「好警察」。<br />\n<br />\n微博"},{"pid":"f0e62f1d7a6f76581b535efacd1d7cff6b512fc0","tid":509596,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23d35ab36428cde6dee442a1766024265aeaa0e","tid":509596,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:23:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bac1bb79b4bff627b57a97cff1535e142417fd7","tid":509596,"uid":71676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"D湖南人真係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5633dcc1ab69a9c80b2a83556857638fe191046","tid":509596,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a066c860aa41a00a8a74179254987e6b89a4690e","tid":509596,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D湖南人真係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地湖南人唔衰得既"},{"pid":"9174370154bae06427553a008696d4b2a77b7b4c","tid":509596,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a066c860aa41a00a8a74179254987e6b89a4690e","tid":509596,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D湖南人真係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地湖南人唔衰得既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"係咪你食左我隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8e0f7dd31027109887b56ca3d3a08a8a3f1762","tid":509596,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a066c860aa41a00a8a74179254987e6b89a4690e","tid":509596,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:36:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D湖南人真係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地湖南人唔衰得既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:44:13.000Z","msg":"係咪你食左我隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c72006f5815d2eb651c4e856380cedf63a08b76","tid":509596,"uid":37463,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:51:15.000Z","msg":"點解塊面會血肉模糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會係求其搵個似樣 , 打到豬頭咁再砌佢生豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"9faf1ca5f54c49a273b3ef1983f2f4c18a1ffd7e","tid":509596,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"湖南真係男盜女娼<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548f10f30487d88381784f5bd2324b161a7348cb","tid":509596,"uid":49707,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:20:00.000Z","msg":"爲了測試美國、香港、中國大陸三地警察的實力，&ldquo;聯合國&rdquo;將三隻兔子放在三個森林中，看三地警察誰先找出兔子。<br />\n<br />\n第一個森林前是美國警察，他們先花整整半天時間開會制定作戰計劃，嚴格分工，然後派特種部隊快速進入森林進行地毯式搜索，結果開會耽擱了時間，兔子跑了，任務失敗！<br />\n<br />\n然後輪到香港警察，他們派了一百多號人和幾十輛警車在森林外一字排開，由帶頭人用喇叭喊話：&ldquo;兔子、兔子，你已經被包圍了，快出來投降&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;半天過去了，沒動靜。飛虎隊進入森林，搜索一遍，沒結果，任務失敗！<br />\n<br />\n最後是中國警察，只有四個，先打了一天麻將，黃昏時一人拿一警棍進入森林，沒五分鐘，聽到森林裏傳來一陣動物的慘叫，中國警察一人抽著一根烟有說有笑的出來，後面拖著一隻鼻青臉腫的熊，熊奄奄一息的說到：&ldquo;不要再打了，我就是兔子&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;"},{"pid":"b08ec06bc6c99804f4e911460f4f10544b54e1a5","tid":509596,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093b155010c37db0a88cff18eb12c50a20303124","tid":509596,"uid":66514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"啲特技化妝都ok"},{"pid":"8af1e7713030a29099a179a86ec799885893cfbc","tid":509596,"uid":9457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T02:00:14.000Z","msg":"其實好似唔係咁簡單<br />\n條湖南佬用嘅槍係靚野<br />\n美制ar15<br />\n意大利製散彈<br />\n仲有熱成像嘅嘅鏡<br />\n全部都係貴野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}